    "body": "steps to show the issue:\r\n1) create 2 tox nodes, A and B\r\n2) A makes a friendrequest to B\r\n3) B accepts friend request\r\n4) A creates 2 NGC private groups\r\n5) B accepts both NGC group invites\r\n6) stop A and B right after both join the first NGC group and save\r\n7) start both A and B with loading their savefiles\r\n8) first NGC group works, the 2nd NGC is forever broken, invite or rejoin does not fix the problem\r\n\r\n\r\nthere is a test program to show the issue: https://gist.github.com/zoff99/ba3df157b95c15a7988f5a40880f8416",
